{
  "stem": "25809.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the moment I pick up those vibrations, they get translated into good, bad, evil, medium, danger, watch out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I get all this in-- just in a flash.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It comes to me whether this is right or wrong.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it has helped me in my business in later years, where I, I can walk into a, into an establishment and immediately sense if this place is doing well, doing bad, mediocre, if there has been a fight, if there has been arguments, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I really did not.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'll, I'll remember when, when my grandmother-- because my grandmother on my mother's side was very liberal.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my grandmother on my father's side was not so liberal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when I went to my grandmother for vacation and I ate some butter or milk with meat and I said, am I allowed to, to do that?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they were not Jewish schools.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, as a matter of fact, I, I-- well, not so much when the war broke out, but when the Germans came into, into Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, I still see myself, ridiculous as it may seem, as a little boy standing at the corner in front of the Apollo Hall-- at that time, I think they still have ice skating there-- and, and the corner of the Apollolaan.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I happen to-- just happen to be there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was always roaming around, going places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nothing seemed to scare me, really, to go anywhere, as a little kid even.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I, I was standing at the corner.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the German occupation came into, into Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And some of the guys were waving to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I kind of waved back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then almost like my other hand wanted to grab my hand down, don't do that.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
